videos.description: The Rockets' Logan Woodside's pass is intercepted by the Mountaineers' Anthony Flory who returns it 19 yards.
videos.headline: App State's Flory picks off Toledo

videos.description: Jalin Moore tumbles into the end zone for a Mountaineers' touchdown.
videos.headline: App State capitalizes on turnover with TD

videos.description: Jalin Moore receives the handoff and runs towards the pylon to extend the Mountaineers' lead.
videos.headline: Moore scores another rushing TD for App State

videos.description: Daetrich Harrington zips down the sidelines for 35 yards putting App State in the red zone, later they kick a field goal that is good.
videos.headline: Harrington runs 35 yards putting Mountaineers in red zone

videos.description: Appalachian State's coach Scott Satterfield discusses his team's defense and Toledo's turnovers in the first half.
videos.headline: Satterfield: 'Our defense has been playing outstanding'

videos.description: Logan Woodside's pass is intercepted by Desmond Franklin who returns it for 35 yards.
videos.headline: App State robs Toledo of possible TD

videos.description: Jalin Moore runs for 31 yards and stiff arms a player to avoid a tackle and runs it home for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Moore squeezes through D for Mountaineers' TD

videos.description: Malik Williams receives the handoff and runs it into the end zone for another Mountaineers' touchdown.
videos.headline: App State extends lead with easy TD

videos.description: Rockets quarterback Logan Woodside throws his third interception of the game to Clifton Duck, who picks it off for no gain.
videos.headline: Toledo's QB Woodside throws another INT

videos.description: The Mountaineers take home the Dollar General Bowl trophy with a 34-0 win.
